; Regression test for issue #2950: commodity format precision enforcement.
;
; Expression-computed amounts (e.g., €10.04 * 0.172) should not trigger
; precision warnings/errors even when the result exceeds the declared
; commodity format precision.

commodity €
    format €1000.000

account Expenses:Tax
account Assets:Cash

2025/06/03 * Tax calculation
    Expenses:Tax                          (€10.04 * 0.172)
    Assets:Cash

test bal --strict
             €-1.727  Assets:Cash
              €1.727  Expenses:Tax
--------------------
                   0
end test
